<div class="_pmvv-vidbox-desc">
<h1 id="overlay-title">Doc</h1>
<p id="overlay-descrip" class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Poor Doc. During the first season of The Chorus Trilogy, he accidentally ends up transported to another dimension, for an undisclosed span of time. When he finally reunites with his comrades, he does not take it well to learn, that no one even noticed that he was gone for that time.	</p>
<div class="rating-row" data-video-id="n4741n">
